ding a high-k oxide within complex van der Waals\nheterostructures could play an important role in future flexible\nmulti-functional van der Waals devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Nov 2018 16:15:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-13"}
