al solutions with the regularized free energy lower than that of the\nstandard diagonal conformal solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Nov 2018 16:21:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2018 17:52:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 12 Dec 2018 17:16:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 6 Jul 2019 08:29:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-22"}
