 F-test 5x2\ncross-validation and nested cross-validation, are recommended for comparing\nmachine learning algorithms when datasets are small.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Nov 2018 15:36:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2018 02:03:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2020 00:59:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-12"}
